CircuitBreaker, RetryManager
public abstract class NetworkPattern
extends InstanceOwnedPattern
implements IRequestUpdateListener
Represents a Pattern that is owned by a MicroserviceInstance and monitors with the network. Patterns of this type listen automatically to every outgoing request of a MicroserviceInstance.

Lion Wagner
